	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi,<br /><br />I just got a UK PAL NES but I live in the US. Can I use the NTSC AC Adapter or do I need a converter?<br /><br />If I need a converter would this work? <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.voltageconverters.com/itemdesc.asp?ic=VC100W">http://www.voltageconverters.com/itemdesc.asp?ic=VC100W</a><!-- m --><br /> <br />Console says: AC9v 1.3A<br /><br />AC Adapter that came with it (not official) says:<br />Input: 240v - 50 Hz<br />Output: 9v - 400mA<br /><br />Not even sure if it's the right adapter but I assume it is?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
